        <h2>About the Conference </h2>
        <p>We are proud to announce the 14th edition of the Cognitive Science Conference, organized by the Cognitive Science Students' Association. This event aims to foster an open and collaborative space for the exchange of ideas, theories, and discoveries from various disciplines within the field of cognitive science. </p>
        <p>Date: May 15-16, 2026</p>
        <p>Venue: Auditorium Maximum, Jagiellonian University</p>
        <p>Join us to explore the forefront of cognitive science and engage with fellow enthusiasts and experts from around the world! </p>
    </section>



    



